&lt;Yugo America Inc>, aunit of &lt;Yugo NV>, said it sold 5,059 cars in February, thefirst month in which sales topped 5,000.    Yugo said the February's sales were 21.2 pct higher thansales in January and 191.4 pct above the 1,736 cars sold in thesame month last year.    Yugo said it has sold a total of 9,233 cars so far in 1987. Reuter&#3;